text: Mirpur Khas is a city in Sindh, Pakistan. Mirpur Khas may also refer to: *Mirpur Khas Division, an administrative unit of Sindh, Pakistan *Mirpur Khas District, a district of Sindh, Pakistan *Mirpur Khas railway station, a railway station in Pakistan ==See also== * * Mirpur (disambiguation)
title: Mirpur Khas (disambiguation)
